### Incident Response — IR-1, IR-3, IR-4

**Policy layer:** IRP updated to include HIPAA breach notification workflow (POA&M item 006 closed, Q1 monitoring).

**Assessment layer:** SAR: IR-1 assessed with POA&M item for HIPAA workflow gap. IR-4 (detection and response capability) assessed through GuardDuty configuration verification.

